'''DaVinci Resolve'''（原名：'''da Vinci Resolve'''，俗稱：'''達芬奇'''、'''達文西'''）是適用於[[MacOS|MacOS]]、[[Windows|Windows]]和[[Linux|Linux]]的調色和[[非線性剪輯|非線性編輯]]的[[視訊剪輯軟體列表|影片剪輯軟體]]，最初由{{le|da Vinci Systems}}開發，後於2009年被[[Blackmagic_Design|Blackmagic Design]]收購。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=DaVinci Resolve 15 is a free, Hollywood-grade video editor|url=https://www.engadget.com/2018-08-22-davinci-resolve-15-free-hollywood-video-editor-review.html|accessdate=2021-02-16|work=Engadget|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109040145/https://www.engadget.com/2018-08-22-davinci-resolve-15-free-hollywood-video-editor-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Blackmagic DaVinci Resolve 15 - The American Society of Cinematographers|url=https://ascmag.com/articles/blackmagic-davinci-resolve-15|accessdate=2021-02-16|work=ascmag.com|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116023511/https://ascmag.com/articles/blackmagic-davinci-resolve-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了該[[軟體|軟體]]的商業版本（稱為DaVinci Resolve Studio）之外，Blackmagic Design還分發了具有減少功能的免費版本，簡稱為DaVinci Resolve（舊稱DaVinci Resolve Lite）。<ref name=":0" />

